txt.en: Gladhir would like you to deal with the local pests of Cirith Ungol.
'That horrible buzzing is much diminished! Was this your doing, [placeholder]? I cannot thank you enough!'
Gladhir has asked you to help exterminate the many pests found in Cirith Ungol.
'You return! I can tell you were successful; the noise is much reduced! Thank you for your service, [placeholder]. One fewer pest out there is one fewer in our food stores later.'
Gladhir has asked you to defeat any insects you come across in Cirith Ungol.
Gladhir can be found in Echad Taerdim, the Ranger camp in Cirith Ungol.\n\nYou should talk to Gladhir.

'I have need of your strength and your will, if you can spare the time.\n\n'We have come to a foul land, corrupted by the dark river below, and ravaged by howling winds above. To make matters worse, we are constantly harassed by the local pests! The incessant buzzing is driving me mad! Please, do me a favour and take care of any insects that cross your path!'
